    <id>webhooks</id>
    <name>Webhooks</name>
    <summary>Integrate your Nextcloud instance with external systems using Webhooks</summary>
    <description><![CDATA[This app allows a Nextcloud instance to call an external service via a HTTP(S) POST request whenever an event of a given type occurs.
    
Outgoing webhooks can be triggered by either Nextcloud's internal events specified in config.php or by Flow actions defined in the admin UI.
]]></description>
